Package: llm-usage-indicator
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10)
Recommends: python3-pip, waybar
Maintainer: llm-usage-indicator contributors
Description: LLM usage indicator for Waybar / system tray
 Tracks Claude / Gemini / OpenAI usage and remaining monthly budget.
 Shows live costs in Waybar or the cross-platform system tray (pystray).
